I’m proud to represent the @thenbpa with @dovemencare to Commit to C.A.R.E about Black men. As a Black man, I am committed to ensuring that Black men and boys are cared for, respected, supported, and protected.

Basketball has afforded me a lot of opportunities, as well as a platform to use my voice for good. One of the best decisions I’ve made was establishing Club 61 (@club61leaders), an initiative that teaches our future leaders how they can make a positive impact in the community.

Support the initiative by taking the pledge at CommitToCARENow.com. #DoveMenCare #NBPA #CommitToCARENow #Club61
